T02TD2466E:141a-1: bandha bi mukto pa de sha n'a ma /
T02TD2466E:141a-3: 'ching ba rnam grol gyi man ngag ces bya ba /
T02TD2466E:141a-4: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2466E:141a-5: kye ho gang gis 'ching bar byed pa'i rgyu //
T02TD2466E:141a-6: de nyid grol bar byed pa'i lam //
T02TD2466E:141a-8: 'ching ba gang yin des grol ba'o //
T02TD2466E:141a-9: 'dod chags bde ba chen por dag / zhe sdang 'od gsal me lce 'bar //
T02TD2466E:141a-10: gti mug rnam par mi rtog nyid //
T02TD2466E:141a-11: dug gsum sku gsum lhun gyis grub //
T02TD2466E:141a-12: 'ching ba rnam grol gyi man ngag ces bya ba /
T02TD2466E:141a-13: rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug shr'i dza ga ta mi tra a'a na nda'i zhal snga nas gsungs pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2466E:141a-15: // / rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug de nyid kyi spyan snga ra lo ts'a ba byams pa'i dpal gyis bal yul glang gser khang du bsgyur ba'o /
